{"tid":807692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"搵唔返以前貢榮個種親切貼地感","createTime":"2018-09-05T17:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T08:21:45.000Z","uid":3857,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e811608169ef0787b6faf8296249508f18d658","tid":807692,"uid":3857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"而家新開咁多台式飲品店 雖然間間都冇乜分別咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係就搵唔返以前貢榮個種貼地感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n閒閒地而家一杯珍珠幻茶都成三四十蚊一杯<br />\n仲要個個排晒隊去買 貢榮以前都係賣十幾蚊杯咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係mk妹店員買杯野飲都閪你面個種態度 而家已經好難搵到<br />\n諗諗下以前樓下屯市間貢榮 次次買都閪你面條mk妹<br />\n做到而家大左肚做人老母都仲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間真係過得好快 小學雞飲到而家中學畢業左幾年<br />\n唔知大家第一杯珍珠幻茶又係幾時呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e0c4e8e2cd374702fe49158e2194dd1463548b","tid":807692,"uid":9205,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"珍珠幻茶係上補習堂先捨得飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48b10742c0a9ba03d32ddd39bd4d803b33f467c","tid":807692,"uid":3857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"13e0c4e8e2cd374702fe49158e2194dd1463548b","tid":807692,"uid":9205,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"珍珠幻茶係上補習堂先捨得飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:08:45.000Z","msg":"以前有個中學同學日日放學都飲一杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f71ec625d56095fc6fa68185addda5b73aab66","tid":807692,"uid":41368,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"而家啲蝗狗茶 杯杯都幾十蚊<br />\n真係唔明邊忽值<br />\n你話Starbucks都可以係因為買佢個咖啡豆配方"},{"pid":"e53695e7081d8d7b688e3b24263ef1c8c1344395","tid":807692,"uid":3857,"like":0,"d